      "span_text": "Mariotto and colleagues [CITATION_1] showed that it took nearly 5 years from the publication of the Nolvadex Adjuvant Tamoxifen Trial report in 1983 for adjuvant use of tamoxifen to reach a 50% level for postmenopausal women, and the adoption of adjuvant polychemotherapy took a similar time course."
